---
title: Plant-Based Protein Messy Janes with Pickled Onion, Roasted Potato Wedges & Vegan Chipotle Mayo
description: Craving the ultimate throwback of the humble sloppy joe—minus the meat? Look no further. This version stars ground, plant-based protein, and is worlds tastier than the ones the lunch lady slung: Think pickled onion, a smoky BBQ sauce, and a side of hearty potato wedges. (We’d still highly recommend keeping a few napkins nearby, though.)
